# Course 1 – Foundations of Cybersecurity

**Google Cybersecurity Professional Certificate**

---

## Course Summary

This course established the foundational concepts of cybersecurity by introducing core security principles, common cyber threats, risk management, industry frameworks, compliance standards, ethical responsibilities, and the essential tools used by security analysts.
Throughout the course, I developed a strong understanding of how organizations protect information systems, assess risk, and respond to security threats. These concepts provide the foundation for the remaining courses in the Google Cybersecurity Professional Certificate.

